A '''destructor beam''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]]-mounted weapon that was essentially a very powerful [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolaser]] and close to the destructive potential of a [[Superlaser/Legends|superlaser]]. One such weapon was installed on the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Courteous]]'', which was tasked with the blockade of the [[ThonBoka]] [[Nebula/Legends|nebula]]. However, the ship and the prototype were destroyed by the [[Oswaft]], ending all research into these shipboard weapons.

